{"tid":791834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【豬隊友】笨賊擲磚破門誤中同夥後腦 丟低同夥落荒而逃","createTime":"2018-08-24T06:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T09:25:47.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6e1569820641d23d6551057f583551726150fe","tid":791834,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:16:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/E6VpFbCVxtU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE6VpFbCVxtU&d=XyYT95eQ3mbSuwd14sle%2BdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=59d72629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E6VpFbCVxtU</a><br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦月初深夜發生一宗「烏龍劫案」，3名劫匪手持磚頭，企圖破門洗劫店鋪。其中一人眼見同伴遲遲敲不破玻璃，決定投擲磚頭幫忙，不料一出手就砸中隊友後腦，害得對方當場昏迷不醒。警衛此時趕至，2名賊人見事敗，於是丟下同伴落荒而逃。<br />\n<br />\n閉路電視畫面可見，當時正值深夜11點許，3人共乘一輛機車到達現場，冷帽男率先下車，手持磚頭朝店家玻璃猛砸。另一同伴為求爭分奪秒，於是從後擲出磚頭，企圖擲碎玻璃。誰知一個不小心誤中副車！磚頭「神準」擊中同伴後腦，冷帽男即時倒地。整個犯案過程僅在短短4秒宣告失敗。<br />\n<br />\n同時，警衛聞聲趕至，2人大難臨頭各自飛，直接分頭逃走，留下冷帽男繼續躺在原地。影片曝光後，引發網民瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/799558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F799558&d=XyYT95eQ3mbSuwd14sle%2BdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a210c127\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F799558&h=c390e9ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/799558</a>"},{"pid":"d467d70bda92f303d1e0cbfc9d80c31e5d062ff8","tid":791834,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"突然醒覺做返好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6369f7f93ab557a0fc50eca8fba0abd4d20cdf92","tid":791834,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:22:56.000Z","msg":"我反而想知咁樣中後腦 條友死左味？ <br />\n唔死都應該植物人"},{"pid":"d481e9f218948a57d829cdd5a84db6fbb1fb7d05","tid":791834,"uid":141917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌"},{"pid":"c661886291d20feac614c75914c07d95ada57c49","tid":791834,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"乜撚野同夥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e21c7997cb0eb532b401ae3eaa7c3494b09ae0","tid":791834,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pgloHmT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpgloHmT.gif&h=75639e6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cc02635f5a115495dd7e7f86de3865add72fd91","tid":791834,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/4-22-2016/HMYIpI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F4-22-2016%2FHMYIpI.gif&h=4f04eb9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個好D"},{"pid":"3acadf05c64701afb2fc822d652c549c4a6640d5","tid":791834,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"Team kill<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b5970e9ed05e6e1d7d8b2351989a26598b295e","tid":791834,"uid":34854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"仲要fing佢兩吓都頭撼地，驚佢唔死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbc318370ba50d367cecea343c0394edc77d8cc","tid":791834,"uid":6473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r